content: I contacted my pset buddy two days ago and they still haven't responded. I went ahead and finished it, but I didn't tick the box at the top. Is that fine? The hw stated I needed to get in contact with course staff.
subject: regarding pset buddy

content: Yes, definitely get started on your own if the buddy does not respond. The only reason we ask you to contact the staff is in case someone else is looking for a buddy -- we could make a new pair.
